Did Ezekiel join
He Who Walks Behind the Rows?

01:16:16.894 --> 01:16:18.895
I don't know.

01:16:18.995 --> 01:16:21.094
He just might have.

01:16:21.194 --> 01:16:23.294
Will we get
to go there?

01:16:26.395 --> 01:16:28.395
I don't think it's
your time yet.

01:17:12.697 --> 01:17:16.297
- Hi.
- You must be Alison.

01:17:16.397 --> 01:17:18.797
- Please, come in.
- Thank you.

